and national celebrity and a shrimping boat captain

4
00:00:17,730 --> 00:00:19,163
以及大学毕业生
and a college graduate,

5
00:00:19,232 --> 00:00:21,666
亚拉巴马州绿茵镇的父老乡亲
the city fathers of Greenbow, Alabama,

6
