So then I got a call from him

11
00:00:37,854 --> 00:00:40,414
说我们再也不用担心没钱花了
saying we don't have to worry about money no more,

12
00:00:40,490 --> 00:00:44,893
我说：“好啊 又少一件麻烦事”
and I said, "That's good. One less thing."

13
00:00:44,962 --> 00:00:46,759
“我有了新的希望…”
# I've got a new hope... #

14
